pageProduct.name: Voost Immunity Blackcurrant Effervescent Tablets 20 Pack
pageProduct.description:
General Information

VOOST Immunity Blackcurrant helps support healthy immune system function with vitamin C 1000mg + Zinc 10mg.

- Support healthy immune system function.
- Reduce the severity and duration of common cold symptoms when taken regularly.
- Reduce free radicals formed in the body.
- Support general health and wellbeing.
- Support skin health.
- support collagen formation.
- Connective tissue production.
- Increase absorption of dietary iron.

Suitable For: Vegan friendly.

Product Claims: No added dairy, lactose, soy or yeast.

Size: 20 Tablets

Flavour: Blackcurrant

Warnings

Keep out of reach of children.
Do not use if tamper evident seal is broken or missing.

IMPORTANT INFORMATION

Less than 0.1g of sugar.
Vitamin and mineral supplements should not replace a balanced diet. If symptoms persist talk to your health professional.

Ingredients

Active Ingredients per tablet:
Ascorbic Acid (Vitamin C) 100mg, Zinc
Zinc (as Zinc Gluconate) 10mg

Contains: Each tablet contains 392mg of Sodium. Sucralose.

Directions

Take 1 tablet daily, dissolved in 200mL of water, or as directed by your health professional. Adults only.

STORAGE INSTRUCTIONS

Store tube tightly closed in a cool, dry place. Store below 25°C.

RECYCLABLE INFORMATION

Please recycle.

Recyclable Packaging?: Yes
